The Genetic Materials market is segmented based on various products and services offered in the industry. Genetic testing kits form a significant part of this market, enabling individuals to gain insights into their genetic makeup for various purposes such as ancestry detection and disease predisposition. Sequencing services play a vital role in analyzing the complete genetic information of an individual or organism. Gene editing tools have revolutionized genetic research and therapies by allowing precise alterations in the genetic code. Genetic screening services are crucial in identifying genetic abnormalities and predispositions to certain diseases.

